displayProperties.name: Kalli, the Corrupted
displayProperties.description: Kalli, an Awoken Techeun who serves Queen Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx and transformed into Kalli, the Corrupted. Free her.

displayProperties.name: Shuro Chi, the Corrupted
displayProperties.description: Shuro Chi, an Awoken Techeun who serves Queen Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx and transformed into Shuro Chi, the Corrupted. Free her.

displayProperties.name: Morgeth, the Spirekeeper
displayProperties.description: Morgeth, the Spirekeeper, an enormous and powerful Taken Ogre, serves as the enforcer of Riven's corruption in the Dreaming City, and the guard of the City's main tower, The Keep of Voices. Destroy them.

displayProperties.name: The Vault
displayProperties.description: A locking mechanism which secures the immensely powerful and treacherous.

displayProperties.name: Riven of a Thousand Voices
displayProperties.description: Riven, the last known Ahamkara, formerly in the service of Mara Sov, was Taken by Oryx. She now corrupts the city from its heart at the behest of the Hive queen, Savathûn.

displayProperties.name: Queenswalk
displayProperties.description: Escape the spire and get the Heart Stone to the Techeun.

displayProperties.name: Crypt Security
displayProperties.description: Penetrate the Bray facility's security protocols and gain access to the Deep Stone Crypt.

displayProperties.name: Atraks-1
displayProperties.description: Counter the self-duplicating, Exo-reborn, Atraks-1.

displayProperties.name: Descent
displayProperties.description: Interrupt the station's Nuclear Descent Protocol and secure the station.

displayProperties.name: Taniks, the Abomination
displayProperties.description: Thwarting Taniks made him grow stronger. Destroy him, once and for all...

displayProperties.name: Confluxes
displayProperties.description: Secure Vex constructs by preventing Vex sacrifices.

displayProperties.name: Oracles
displayProperties.description: Counter the Oracles' song or be marked for negation and lost to time.

displayProperties.name: The Templar
displayProperties.description: An extremely powerful Vex Hydra, The Templar is unique in it being a creature out of time. As such, it can manipulate reality in accordance to the Oracles' design.

displayProperties.name: Gatekeepers
displayProperties.description: Protectors of the Glass Throne, the Gatekeepers are Vex Hydras who stand as the Throne's last defence.

displayProperties.name: Atheon, Time's Conflux
displayProperties.description: The Axis Mind responsible for bridging the Vex's own calculations into existence.

displayProperties.name: Acquisition
displayProperties.description: Your eyes are always closed. Do you not see what's right in front of you? Those who fail to see the truth will drown in it.

displayProperties.name: Collection
displayProperties.description: SCORN. They eat away at the decay within a shell of. SCORN. Truth exists all around outside the shell of. SCORN.

displayProperties.name: Exhibition
displayProperties.description: Did you think you were the observer? Or did you believe you pulled the strings? Now's your chance—with artifacts of fate, you can make them dance.

displayProperties.name: Dominion
displayProperties.description: The Upended is alive. You have no more tasks ahead. Lie down and embrace the darkness beyond your final days.

displayProperties.name: Evade the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Evade Voltaic Overload charges and pursue the Consecrated Mind.

displayProperties.name: Summon the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Bypass Vex confluxes and force out the Consecrated Mind from hiding.

displayProperties.name: Defeat the Consecrated Mind
displayProperties.description: Once and for all, defeat the Consecrated Mind.

displayProperties.name: The Sanctified Mind
displayProperties.description: A Vex Axis Mind, the Sanctified Mind amasses control over many Vex. Defeat it to prevent further incursions by the Sol Divisive outside of the Black Garden.

displayProperties.name: Open the Portal
displayProperties.description: Gain access to the Dreadnaught's inner sanctum.

displayProperties.name: Basilica
displayProperties.description: Influence hive ritual magic by controlling annihilator totems.

displayProperties.name: Warpriest
displayProperties.description: Defeat Oryx's Warpriest before he destroys you.

displayProperties.name: Golgoroth
displayProperties.description: Subdue the abomination.

displayProperties.name: The Daughters
displayProperties.description: Interrupt the the sisters' concentration.

displayProperties.name: Oryx
displayProperties.description: Dethrone the king.

displayProperties.name: Cataclysm
displayProperties.description: Beat back Shadow Legion forces and pursue Nezarec.

displayProperties.name: Scission
displayProperties.description: Enter the Root.

displayProperties.name: Macrocosm
displayProperties.description: Align worlds and defeat the Explicator.

displayProperties.name: Nezarec
displayProperties.description: End the nightmare and defeat Nezarec.

displayProperties.name: The Abyss
displayProperties.description: Uncover the illuminated path in the darkness.

displayProperties.name: Oversoul Throne Bridge
displayProperties.description: Traverse the bridge and climb the Throne.

displayProperties.name: Ir Yût, the Deathsinger
displayProperties.description: Strike down the witch, silence their Deathsong.

displayProperties.name: Crota, Son of Oryx
displayProperties.description: Use Crota's most powerful weapon against him.

displayProperties.name: Search for safe passage
displayProperties.description: "Show me your cunning…"

displayProperties.name: Vorgeth, the Boundless Hunger
displayProperties.description: "Shape your schemes into reality…"

displayProperties.name: Dûl Incaru, the Eternal Return
displayProperties.description: "Enter the infinite…"

displayProperties.name: Necropolis
displayProperties.description: Turn the blades of the enemy against them.

displayProperties.name: Chamber of Suffering
displayProperties.description: Endure the Chamber of Suffering.

displayProperties.name: Zulmak, Instrument of Torment
displayProperties.description: Slay Zulmak, Instrument of Torment.

displayProperties.name: Defeat the Phalanx Echo
displayProperties.description: Confront the Phalanx Echo, a part of the Nine's answer to your question.

displayProperties.name: Escape
displayProperties.description: Find a way forward.

displayProperties.name: Defeat the Kell Echo
displayProperties.description: Confront the Kell Echo, a part of the Nine's answer to your question.

displayProperties.name: The Emissary
displayProperties.description: Collect your reward from the Nine.

displayProperties.name: Phry'zhia, The Insatiable
displayProperties.description: Turn the cycle of greed against your enemies.

displayProperties.name: Fallen Shield
displayProperties.description: Fire Servitor remains at the Fallen shield.

displayProperties.name: Captain Avarokk the Covetous
displayProperties.description: Turn the cycle of greed against Captain Avarokk the Covetous.

displayProperties.name: Sorrow Bearer
displayProperties.description: "You were born only to suffer, because I could not set aside that which I knew was a trap. My curiosity is a poison flowing through my veins, curdling my heart, rotting my mind. And yet, I do nothing to stop it."

displayProperties.name: Vault
displayProperties.description: "I beg you, don't do this."

displayProperties.name: Calus's Greatest Shame
displayProperties.description: "Is this what I have done? Once, she looked at me with adoring eyes. I was her world, and she my stars. How have I made her into this? Have I been so blind? So selfish? What have I done?"

displayProperties.name: Ascend the Spire
displayProperties.description: Open a route via the grav lift to the Spire peak, where the Pillory signal is being sourced.

displayProperties.name: Silence the Siren
displayProperties.description: Destroy Akelous, the Siren's Current before it can complete the Pillory protocol and imprison Rasputin's subminds.

displayProperties.name: Prompt Critical
displayProperties.description: Destroy Persys, Primordial Ruin and prevent the complex's reactor core meltdown from causing irreparable damage.

displayProperties.name: Break the Ritual
displayProperties.description: Unravel the Lucent Hive ritual.

displayProperties.name: Defeat the Shield of Savathûn
displayProperties.description: Defeat Ecthar, the Shield of Savathûn.

displayProperties.name: Defeat Šimmumah ur-Nokru
displayProperties.description: Defeat the lightforged necromancer, Šimmumah ur-Nokru.

displayProperties.name: Mysterious Challenger
displayProperties.description: A corrupted Knight stands between you and answers. Meet their challenge, leave them broken, but beware latent curses.

displayProperties.name: Wailing Tempest
displayProperties.description: Wish for warmth, brave the frigid winds, and silence the Locus of Wailing Grief that sustains them.

displayProperties.name: Quell the Corruption
displayProperties.description: "You have taken my vengeance. My task is done, Naeem's wish fulfilled. Come then, slay me. Let it end." —Hefnd
